    <HediffDef ParentName="DiseaseBase">
		<defName>aAS_WAE_OdEnergy_StorageCapacity</defName>
        <hediffClass>AncientSpecies.Hediff_OdEnergy</hediffClass>
		<label>オドエネルギー</label>
		<defaultLabelColor>(0.65,1,0.65)</defaultLabelColor>
        <scenarioCanAdd>false</scenarioCanAdd>
        <description>オドエネルギーを体内に貯蔵、留める能力。オドエネルギーにより平時から身体能力が向上するだけでなく、貯蔵したオドを使うことでさらに強化することが出来る。貯蔵できる容量と身体能力の強化度合いは、どれだけオドエネルギーの操作に習熟しているかによって決まる。未熟な者でも年月により延びていく。</description>
		<isBad>false</isBad><!-- バッドステータスか -->
		<everCurableByItem>false</everCurableByItem><!-- 治癒可能か -->
		<maxSeverity>5.0</maxSeverity>
		<comps>
            <li Class="AncientSpecies.AS_HediffCompProperties_OdSystem">
                <ticksToRandomize>60000~180000</ticksToRandomize> <!-- 1-3 days -->
                <notifyMessage>{PAWN_labelShort}'s infant illness went from {1} to {2}.</notifyMessage>
                <odTypes>
                    <li>
                        <labelPrefix>ハーフ種族</labelPrefix>
                        <descriptionExtra>that are life threatening without exceptional medical care and glitterworld medicine.</descriptionExtra>
                        <startSeverity>0</startSeverity>
                        <maxServerity>5</maxServerity>
                        <severityPerDay>0.017</severityPerDay>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <labelPrefix>古代種</labelPrefix>
                        <descriptionExtra>that are life threatening without good medical care and standard medicine.</descriptionExtra>
                        <startSeverity>3</startSeverity>
                        <maxServerity>7</maxServerity>
                        <severityPerDay>0.017</severityPerDay>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <labelPrefix>原始種</labelPrefix>
                        <descriptionExtra>that can be life threatening without basic medicine and tending.</descriptionExtra>
                        <startSeverity>5</startSeverity>
                        <maxServerity>10</maxServerity>
                        <severityPerDay>0.017</severityPerDay>
                    </li>
                </odTypes>
            </li>
            <li Class="HediffCompProperties_TendDuration">
                <baseTendDurationHours>18</baseTendDurationHours>
                <tendOverlapHours>6</tendOverlapHours>
                <severityPerDayTended>-.35</severityPerDayTended>
            </li>
            <li Class="HediffCompProperties_Immunizable"> <!-- to provide some inevitability -->
                <immunityPerDaySick>.1</immunityPerDaySick>
                <severityPerDayImmune>-0.70</severityPerDayImmune>
                <immunityPerDayNotSick>-0.70</immunityPerDayNotSick>
                <hidden>true</hidden>
            </li>
            </comps>
